### Todo API Test Examples
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or copy to Postman/Insomnia

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Get API Documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### Create a new todo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy groceries",
  "description": "Milk, eggs, bread, vegetables",
  "completed": false
}

###

### Create another todo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Finish project report",
  "description": "Complete the Q2 analysis report",
  "completed": false
}

###

### Create a third todo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Call dentist",
  "description": "Schedule appointment for next week"
}

###

### Get all todos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/todos

###

### Get a specific todo (replace :id with actual ID, e.g., 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/todos/1

###

### Get only completed todos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/todos?completed=true

###

### Get only incomplete todos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/todos?completed=false

###

### Update a todo (full update)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/todos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy groceries and cook dinner",
  "description": "Milk, eggs, bread, vegetables, chicken",
  "completed": true
}

###

### Partially update a todo (mark as completed)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/todos/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "completed": true
}

###

### Partially update a todo (update title only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/todos/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Call dentist - URGENT"
}

###

### Delete a specific todo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/todos/1

###

### Delete all todos
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/todos

###

### Test validation - empty title (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "This should fail"
}

###

### Test validation - missing title (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "This should fail"
}

###

### Test 404 - non-existent todo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/todos/999

###

### Test 404 - invalid endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/invalid-endpoint

###